data.description: This is a gorgeous & spacious newly updated split level 5 bedroom 2 bathroom home is nestle on a quiet street just east of Beverly located blocks from Morgan Park High School and Morgan Park Academy and   2 blocks west of Interstate 57 Features The property features Maple Shaker cabinets, stainless steel appliances, & quartz countertop. This tri-level home has beautiful wide planked hardwood flooring with a natural finish where the upper level consists of 3 bedrooms and a full bath.  The main level consists of separate living & dining area, along with the kitchen, in addition there is a finished basement for optimized space. The finished basement gives you an additional 2 bedrooms, a bathroom, & a separate laundry area.  Because the back yard is so huge, you can't help but picture yourself having family & friend gatherings. It has additional storage space in a new storage shed. This Morgan Park home is close to  Metra, Cta, and I57  & The Marshfield Plaza for all your shopping and restaurant needs. It is a must see!
